BREAST-COMPOSITION: fibro fatty and glandular breast parenchyma (ACR C)
FINDINGS: a few small, well-defined soft opacities are seen in the upper and lower quadrants of the breast. These findings suggest a probably benign lesion (BIRADS 3).
